desc: Rubee's Wraps provide a breathable cover that allows you to naturally preserve your food & decrease food wastage without plastic. Eco-friendly and hand-crafted in rural NSW using 100% cotton material, a special mixture of jojoba oil, food grade beeswax and dammar resin, all soured within Australia.

layout.text: Beeswax wraps handcrafted in rural NSW using Australian sourced materials.
